nodes.text: The Naboo Zoo was a zoo located on the planet of Naboo.

This zoo loaned a male voorpak to the Jedi academy on Coruscant during Roan Novachez's second year of attendance there, which the students named Voorpee. Later in the school year, a pair of class bullies stuffed Voorpee in a locker and Novachez, incorrectly blamed for the crime, was forced to write a letter of apology to the Naboo Zoo.
